{"id":1411,"date":"2022-03-16T16:59:00","date_gmt":"2022-03-16T16:59:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1411"},"modified":"2022-03-15T18:15:42","modified_gmt":"2022-03-15T18:15:42","slug":"perform-basic-container-management-such-as-running-starting-stopping-and-listing-running-containers","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1411","title":{"rendered":"Perform basic container management such as running, starting, stopping, and listing running containers"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>We&#8217;ve successfully used podman and scopeo to find, pull and inspect the container. Now it&#8217;s time to use this container for something practical. To do that you obviously need to know first few basic things like: starting, stopping and listing containers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To demonstrate this management commands, let&#8217;s make an apache server and run a site.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>First, let&#8217;s find apache server container with podman help<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman search httpd | less<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"56\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=640%2C56&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1422\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=1024%2C89&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=300%2C26&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=768%2C67&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=24%2C2&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=36%2C3&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?resize=48%2C4&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-35.png?w=1256&amp;ssl=1 1256w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now pick one and pull it as I showed you in the previous post. Just in the case you forgot, you have to type<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman pull registry.access.redhat.com\/rhscl\/httpd-24-rhel7<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"152\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?resize=640%2C152&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1423\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?resize=300%2C71&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?resize=768%2C182&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?resize=24%2C6&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?resize=36%2C9&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-36.png?resize=48%2C11&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Run a container<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To run a container we will again use podman command with few new parameters that I&#8217;ll explain.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman run -d --name httpd_test registry.access.redhat.com\/rhscl\/httpd-24-rhel<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"40\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?resize=640%2C40&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?w=906&amp;ssl=1 906w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?resize=300%2C19&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?resize=768%2C47&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?resize=24%2C1&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?resize=36%2C2&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-37.png?resize=48%2C3&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Stop a container<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman stop httpd_test<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>List running\/non-running containers<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can either list all container or just the containers that are running.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To list just the running containers, we use <em>podman ps<\/em> command<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman ps<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"61\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=640%2C61&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1426\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=1024%2C98&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=300%2C29&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=768%2C73&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=24%2C2&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=36%2C3&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?resize=48%2C5&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-39.png?w=1139&amp;ssl=1 1139w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To list all the containers, you have to add -a flag to the command<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman ps -a<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"85\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=640%2C85&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1425\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=1024%2C136&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=300%2C40&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=768%2C102&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=36%2C5&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-38.png?w=1131&amp;ssl=1 1131w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>List images<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">podman images<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"69\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?resize=640%2C69&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1427\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?w=886&amp;ssl=1 886w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?resize=300%2C32&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?resize=768%2C82&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?resize=36%2C4&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/image-40.png?resize=48%2C5&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the next post, I&#8217;ll explain to you how to run a service, which finally lead us to real life examples of container world.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We&#8217;ve successfully used podman and scopeo to find, pull and inspect the container. Now it&#8217;s [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1401,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[51],"tags":[496,498,220,354,355],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/rhsa-Manage-containers.png?fit=1280%2C720&ssl=1","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1411"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1411"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1411\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1428,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1411\/revisions\/1428"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/media\/1401"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=1411"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcategories&post=1411"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Ftags&post=1411"}],"curies":[{"name":